div.div:
How can you fall in love when you can’t even hold hands? Due to a childhood curse, anything that the Duke touches will die—which makes his flirty maid’s behavior all the more shocking! Is there a way for the Duke and his companions to somehow break the curse, or is he doomed to a life where love is forever out of his reach?
(Source: Funimation)

I, the protagonist, was just an ordinary high school girl, but suddenly I was reincarnated as a spider monster in a fantasy world. Not only that, but I awakened in a dungeon filled with vicious monsters. Armed with only my human knowledge and my overwhelming positivity, I'm forced to use spiderwebs and traps to defeat far stronger monsters just to stay alive... So begins the labyrinth survival story of a girl with incredible mental strength living as one of the lowest-ranked beasts!
(Source: Crunchyroll)

Yoon Hana finds out that her family is moving out just before the high school entrance ceremony. At first she as worried about transferring to a new school, but her bright personality prevents her from being depressed for too long. However, the first day at the new school doesn't go quiet well how she would imagine. She quickly encounters trouble with her intimidating desk mate, Lee Chang-wook! But soon Hana starts to learn that there's more to Chang-wook than meets the eye. This is the story of the sunny Hana's project to help the gloomy Chang-wook make friends!
Tensei Shitara Dai Nana Ouji Dattanode, Kimamani Majutsu wo Kiwamemasu
Adventure, Comedy, Ecchi, Fantasy, Romance, Slice of Life

Prince Lloyd wasn't always a prince...in fact, his previous life is one he remembers perfectly: he was a sorcerer, of sorts. So when he was forced to reincarnate, he decided to continue his studies, prince of the realm or no! But his new life has its own sets of challenges...including being a 10-year-old! What's the 7th prince/sorcerer to do?!

(Source: Kodansha USA)

div.span: Turbulent Adventurers are Introverted, Observant, Feeling, Prospecting and Turbulent. Adventurers are flexible and charming, always ready to explore and experience something new. They tend to have open minds, approaching life, new experiences, and people with grounded warmth.
Mostly Introverted. Likely prefers fewer, yet deep and meaningful, social interactions and feels drawn to calmer environments.
Mostly Observant. Likely pragmatic and down-to-earth, with a strong focus on what is happening or very likely to happen.
Mostly Feeling. Likely values emotional expression and sensitivity, prioritizing empathy, social harmony, and cooperation.
Mostly Prospecting. Likely very good at improvising and adapting. Tends to be flexible and values novelty above stability.
Mostly Turbulent. Likely self-conscious, sensitive to stress, success-driven, perfectionistic, and eager to improve.
